\clearpage
\section*{Choice of game}
\begin{flushleft}

We chose the game Dots and Boxes because: \newline
\begin{enumerate}
 Dots and Boxes fulfils the criteria for a combinatorial game. It is relatively simple to learn and play. After spending few hours on playing this game, we realized that this game isn't as simple as it appears to. We found it is really fun to play and think about the strategy to defeat the bot. It is a challenge for us to  make the algorithm for computer to play, but we all think it is interesting to write a plyer for this game. 
\end{enumerate}

\end{flushleft}

