\section*{Program type}
We are going to write a player program for the Dots And Boxes. 
We will try to improve upon the code and algorithm, reach the level of a solver hopefully.

\section*{Division of work}
Yan Liu is going to build the User interface, Zihao Wang and Xinyue Chen are going to conceive the algorithm about the computer player and write it to code, David Wang is going to write code about the game like score and rule.
We will look up some algorithm from online and learn from it, in order to come up with our own ideas. There are some simple codes online for Dots and Boxes, but those code are written for user playing against other user. We may learn some code, but we need to write most of the code by ourselves. We anticipate that about 70 percent of the code will be written by us explicitly. \newline


